                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">German Ambassador</gloss> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">German Embassy</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-02-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 28, 1899</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">memorandum.</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Owing to recent menaces of German interests in China it appears probable that the
                    last German warship, now in the Philippines, will be recalled from there. In
                    this case the German Government has expressed the hope that the protection of
                    life and property of German citizens, and of such people enjoying German
                    protection in the Philippines, will be undertaken by the United States
                    forces.</p>
            </div>
